subject: Snow and Snowstorms
X Games
lead_paragraph: Simon Dumont, one of the word’s elite freeskiers, will again attempt to break a world record when he goes for 32.5 feet of air above a snowboard quarterpipe built near his hometown of Bethel, Me.
